# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  CareerForge AI — Frontend Environment Variables
#
#  The frontend no longer needs any API keys — Groq and the
#  YouTube Data API are both called from the backend now, which
#  is the only place that holds real credentials (see
#  backend/.env.example instead).
#
#  This file only matters if you deploy the backend somewhere
#  other than http://localhost:5000. For local development you
#  can leave this file / a .env entirely unused — vite.config.js
#  already proxies /api to the backend.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# VITE_API_URL=https://your-deployed-backend.example.com/api
